OL,3,CInterest rates held at 5.25% but Bank
OL,4,Cof England 'optimistic' about cuts
OL,6,FBut he added: "We need to see more
OL,7,Fevidence that inflation will stay low
OL,8,Fbefore we can cut interest rates."
OL,10,FIn a strong signal that the tide is
OL,11,Fturning among the rate-setters, two
OL,12,Fmembers of the Bank's nine-person
OL,13,FMonetary Policy Committee (MPC) voted
OL,14,Ffor interest rates to be cut by 0.25
OL,15,Fpercentage points, to 5%.
OL,17,FThe MPC members, Swati Dhingra and
OL,18,FDave Ramsden, feel Consumer Prices
OL,19,FIndex (CPI) inflation is already on a
OL,20,Ffirm downward path and there is no
OL,21,Fneed to delay reducing borrowing costs.
