OL,3,CInterest rates held at 5.25% but Bank
OL,4,Cof England 'optimistic' about cuts
OL,6,FBut the committee signalled it is
OL,7,Flooking for greater progress on key
OL,8,Feconomic indicators, which are
OL,9,Fcontinuing to put pressure on the
OL,10,Foverall inflation rate.
OL,12,FThese include wage growth and services
OL,13,Finflation, which remain relatively
OL,14,Fpersistent.
OL,16,FCrucially, the MPC will be able to
OL,17,Fassess upcoming data releases,
OL,18,Fincluding April and May's official
OL,19,Finflation and jobs figures, before its
OL,20,Fnext meeting in June.
